## Tech Stack  
- **Backend & Frontend**: Python 
- **Package Manager**: [`uv`](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/)  
- **Frameworks/Libraries**:  
  - FastAPI (backend)
  - Reflex (Web GUI)
  - Pydantic (JSON parsing and serialization)
  - Pandas (Excel parsing)  
  - OpenAPI's Python client (LLMs)
